WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:13.581 --> 00:00:15.581
Hi everybody !

00:00:18.655 --> 00:00:21.898
I will present a really cool application, MyVideoZone

00:00:22.052 --> 00:00:24.749
which allows you to manage your movie collection easily.

00:00:26.758 --> 00:00:31.104
You can add or delete a category of film.

00:00:33.037 --> 00:00:36.722
You can of course add a movie, just like that.

00:00:36.639 --> 00:00:37.996
You have several options to do it.

00:00:38.075 --> 00:00:43.691
If you have the movie on DVD, you can 
 scan the QR code directly from here.

00:00:43.691 --> 00:00:52.475
Then the application will automatically shows you the information of the film.

00:00:53.352 --> 00:00:59.112
The actors, director, year, summary etc.

00:01:00.622 --> 00:01:03.249
You can choose the category of film.

00:01:06.241 --> 00:01:10.273
If you have the movie on your phone or tablet

00:01:11.083 --> 00:01:18.497
You can select it and then be able 
 to view it directly in the application.

00:01:19.091 --> 00:01:23.505
You can also add your personal opinion, and to whom you lent the film.

00:01:29.299 --> 00:01:32.722
You have a second possibility when you add a movie.

00:01:35.734 --> 00:01:42.030
You can simply write the name of the movie and click search.

00:01:43.853 --> 00:01:46.620
Choose the film that matches.

00:01:47.321 --> 00:01:52.390
The application will display all the information about the film.

00:02:00.940 --> 00:02:07.690
When you go into one of the categories 
 you see an overview of the films.

00:02:08.273 --> 00:02:10.560
By clicking above you have more information.

00:02:12.616 --> 00:02:16.350
Criticism of the press, spectators, you own opinion, the summary etc..

00:02:21.478 --> 00:02:24.340
You can also if you edit or add a 
 video, choose on wich format it is.

00:02:27.229 --> 00:02:33.060
If it's a DVD, BlueRay, on the computer, a USB stick etc.

00:02:37.178 --> 00:02:45.180
Directly from there you can also watch the movie (if 
 you have it on your phone or tablet)

00:02:45.442 --> 00:02:47.910
or see the trailer!

00:02:48.521 --> 00:02:56.340
So that all the main features of the application, I 
 invite you to download it (it's in english too)

00:02:57.719 --> 00:03:01.200
You can with it, manage your movie collection easily!

00:03:03.835 --> 00:03:11.620
Note that you can export and import data directly from the application settings.

00:03:15.151 --> 00:03:20.930
You can update to the pro version if you 
 do not want ads in the application !

00:03:22.846 --> 00:03:26.200
Have a nice day! Feel free to subscribe to my YouTube channel

00:03:26.201 --> 00:03:29.190
and follow me on Twitter, Facebook and Google +

00:03:28.364 --> 00:03:29.880
See you soon, bye !

